
A systematic technique is described for selecting an appropriate mode of zzso pacing on the basis of 10 clinical zzso A computer model of the selection process was developed with input from more than 41 zzso physicians, and implemented together with a database management system for keeping track of mode selections and identifying cases in which the modes selected by the zzso differed from those recommended by the zzso The selection technique, which can be used without a computer, is presented in detail with a zzso representation of the model and an explanation of the rationale behind each of its 39 possible zzso 

